6th March 2009

Sahana - README
===============

Sahana is a Free and Open Source Disaster Management System.It mainly facilitates management of Missing people, disaster victims, Managing and administrating various organisations, managing camps and managing requests and assistance in the proper distribution of resources.

version - trunk
----------------
