Requirements:
    o php 5.0 or later
    o MySQL 4.1 or later
    o Apache web server 1.3 or later
    o latest php5-gd libs
    o latest php5-gettext libs for localization

Demo:

        http://demo.sahana.lk/

Download:
    
    o Download the latest Sahana release in your preferred format from,
        
        http://download.sahana.lk

    o In order to get Sahana on Debian GNU/Linux or a Debian based distro 
      (like Ubuntu, Knoppix, Mepis, etc.), you can add following to your 
      /etc/apt/sources.list,

        deb http://sahana.lk/apt stable main

      and do,

        apt-get update && apt-get install sahana
      
      to upgrade from an older Sahana version to a newer version,

        apt-get upgrade
        
        
Install:

    Please see the INSTALL file.

Support:

    Sahana is developed through a distributed development environment. Therefore, e-mail is
    the preferred way to discuss various items. Most of the conversations regarding the 	development of Sahana
    is managed through the "sahana-maindev" mailinglist.
    
        https://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/sahana-maindev

    For those who want more general discussion on Humanitarian ICT,

        http://groups.yahoo.com/group/humanitarian-ict/

    The Sahana community also hangs out on an IRC channel,

        #sahana on freenode

Other:

    Sahana specification,

        http://www.reliefsource.org/foss/index.php/Sahana

    Sahana Development Wiki for contributors,

        http://www.sahana.lk/wiki/


Enjoy!!!

    Sahana Community

